    "description": "Double your main protein. This smoky, spicy lahmacun is Turkey's answer to pizza. You'll simmer tender beef mince with smoked paprika, cumin and chilli before spreading it over crispy tortillas. Dollop with garlicky yoghurt and pickled onion for a tangy finish.",
